{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said that he exposed this-- he wasn't worried about the Jewish people dying, but he said that he has no labor force to send him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He said that you should take better care of forces than what you did, and he's not going to send any more people to him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He didn't have any more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were all engaged in-- in other areas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But this heavily damaged our unit as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My platoon had very heavy losses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were a very interesting unit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The number of people there was approximately 160, but the age was from 14 to 65, because they brought these people in from factories.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The mix was very interesting, because there were people like me who tried to just survive, there were students, there were executives of factories who went into their factory, and there were Jewish workers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "To my astonishment, the first time in my life I met these Jewish workers who were working in those factories.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And some of the people who were there were very influential, and they managed to arrange with the ministry that our unit was transferred from this factory to Szob in a mine that produced stone in a stone mine.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And Szob was outside of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It looked as a very innocent place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "However, we were not very lucky with that, because Szob had a railway bridge which went through a river.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this railway bridge served the line to Berlin, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the German army from the Balkans started to withdraw late in August.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And military trains were coming practically continuously, leaving out 50, 100 meters in between two trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the Allied were bombing that bridge day and night.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
